post.title: Volunteers Needed for Senior Band Night

post.content:
Dear Band Families,

We only have a few weeks before we will be honoring the senior band members. On Friday, October 7, 2016, dinner for them and their immediate family will be served at 5:15PM, right after practice and before the football game. The rest of the band will enjoy pizza, bakery and beverages. Obviously, we need a few volunteers to help make sure this event goes smoothly.

Please view the Signup Genius link and if you could help out it would be greatly appreciated.

Thank you,

Helen Kelly
Hospitality
